OL,3,CTributes to woman killed in hospital
OL,4,Ccar park crash
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a mother-of-
OL,7,Ffour who died following a five-vehicle
OL,8,Fcollision in a hospital car park.
OL,10,FMichelle Barford, who was in her 50s,
OL,11,Fwas struck as she was walking in car
OL,12,Fpark B of Stoke Mandeville hospital in
OL,13,FAylesbury, Buckinghamshire.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called just
OL,16,Fafter 2.20pm on Friday, 10 July.
OL,18,FShe was taken to hospital but died
OL,19,Ffrom her injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
